com.a0xffffffff.dinesum

Class RequestTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.a0xffffffff.dinesum.RequestTracker

  • public class RequestTracker
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores lists of requests received from the FirebaseManager sorted based on if the user created the request, if the user claimed/completed the request, or if the request is in the vicinity of the user.
